<div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-width-1-2@m">
    <div class="uk-card-header">
        <div class="uk-grid-small uk-flex-middle" uk-grid>
            <div class="uk-width-auto">
            <% if @user.image? %>
              <%= image_tag @user.image.url, size: 200 %> 
            <% else %>
                 <img class="mr-2 rounded" src="<%= gravatar_url(@user, { size: 50 }) %>" alt="">
            <% end %>    
            </div>
            <div class="uk-width-expand">
                <h3 class="uk-card-title uk-margin-remove-bottom"><%= @user.name %></h3>
                    <ul class="nav nav-tabs nav-justified mb-3">
                       <li><%= link_to '読んだ本', reads_path %></li>
                       <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">読んでいる本</a></li>
                       <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">読みたい本</a></li>
                       <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">フォロー</a></li>
                       <li class="nav-item"><a href="#" class="nav-link">フォロワー</a></li>
                    </ul>
                <p class="uk-text-meta uk-margin-remove-top"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="uk-width-expand">
               <p uk-margin>
                 <a class="uk-button uk-button-default"><%= link_to '書籍登録', new_read_path %></a>
               </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="uk-card-body">
        <p>ここにユーザの自己紹介文などがあればいいのかもしれない。入れるのを検討してみよう</p>
    </div>
    <div class="uk-card-footer">
        <a href="#" class="uk-button uk-button-text">ここは機能として追加の予定はないのでのちのち削除予定</a>
    </div>

</div>

